<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-12-30T22:09:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-01-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="629" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d629">
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                    </head>
                    <p>The United Nations General Assembly held its second meeting of the day from 3
                        to 6:30 p. m. on October 6; for the record, see U.N. document A/PV.293. No
                        voting took place, as the discussion on the draft resolutions continued.</p>
